Database data is lost after container restart. Why?

Answer:
Because no volume was used.

Fix:
docker run -v db-data:/var/lib/mysql mysql
Use Docker volumes for persistence

Two containers need to communicate. How?
Answer:

Create a custom network:

docker network create mynet
docker run --network mynet --name app myapp
docker run --network mynet --name db mysql

Then access DB using:
db:3306

